As Drag Strip grabs a good piece of his leader hoisting him up, he turns
his head to the right, and is met by the gun of Astroblast, who is fully
transfrom. "Suppose I was to accidently blow youre head off" he replies, in
almost the same tone as Drag Strip.

"Just asking" spits Drag Strip as he and Speedbreaker carry Motormaster
into the base. " Well you'd better hope my mood improves after I recharge"
Astroblast retorts, "Or I might tell Motormaster of youre treachery".

Somewhat away from his comerades Dead-End turns around to follow them. "Who
cares" he states.
